ers.  Illustrated with more than forty photographs of physical remains, this book promises to become an essential guide to a historical era of profound influence"--cProvided by publisher.  a32 34 0aChurch historyyPrimitive and early church, ca. 30-600. 0aChurch historyyMiddle Ages, 600-1500.  a7bcbccorignewd1eecipf20gy-gencatlg0 aacquireb2 shelf copiesxpolicy default  brk11 2014-06-02irk11 2014-06-02 ONIX to Deweywxl04 2014-06-02  aAnn-Marie Imbornoni; phone: 203-432-0903; email: ann-marie.imbornoni@yale.edu; bc: meredith.phillips@yale.edu  aBR 162.3 M33 2015wLCc1i0163980491100d3/28/2017e3/9/2017lON_SHELFmNEWMANn7rYsYtBOOKu2/18/2015  aBR 162.3 M33 2015wLCc1i33338000171871d10/14/2016lON_SHELFmCONCORDSEMq1rYsYtBOOKu7/11/201601ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2003097442bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/17466904